query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1) NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1 acc) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('2010',
'2013',
'books',
'development',
'harry-potter',
'sharepoint-enterprise',
'sharepoint-online',
'star-trek',
'story-identification',
'wiring',
'workflow')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('diy',
'scifi',
'sharepoint',
'webapps')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Autobiographer',
'Citizen Patrol',
'Critic',
'Famous Question',
'Informed',
'Necromancer',
'Nice Answer',
'Nice Question',
'Notable Question',
'Popular Question',
'Student',
'Supporter',
'Teacher',
'Tumbleweed',
'Yearling')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 10
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
